<plot>Paul is a young Jewish man whose obsession with the Holocaust interferes with his love life. His long-distance relationship with Dunia, a non-Jewish woman from the former Yugoslavia is threatened by his readiness to see Hitler everywhere, even in himself. When Dunia finally makes the trip to New York, Paul must overcome his detached intellectualism and make an emotional leap.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?334412</url></doc>
